data.description: Charming 4 Bedroom Home with Open Floor Plan near Crowfield Golf Club. Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Goose Creek, SC! This exquisite 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem is nestled on a spacious .26-acre lot in the sought-after neighborhood, just a stone's throw away from the prestigious Crowfield Golf Club. With its inviting open floor plan and modern amenities, this home is perfect for both relaxation and entertainment.Key Features: - 4 spacious bedrooms providing ample space for your family's comfort. - 2 well-appointed bathrooms designed for convenience and style. - Kitchen boasting a center island, making meal preparation a joyous experience. - Expansive living area seamlessly flowing into the dining space, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. - Abundant natural light throughout, highlighting the beauty of the interior. - Awe-inspiring community walking trails perfect for afternoon strolls and exploration. - Serene lakes scattered throughout the neighborhood, adding to the picturesque charm. - Enjoy outdoor leisure with a play park, community pools, and a clubhouse - all just steps away. - Golf enthusiasts will relish the proximity to Crowfield Golf Club, with memberships available for those with a passion for the greens. - Convenient access to I-26, making commuting a breeze and opening up a world of possibilities.  Indulge in the quintessential suburban lifestyle while maintaining access to urban conveniences. Whether you're taking leisurely walks on the neighborhood trails, enjoying the stunning lakes, or embracing the vibrant community amenities, this home offers an exceptional living experience that you'll cherish.  Don't miss your chance to call this wonderful property your own. Schedule a showing today and discover the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience in this charming Goose Creek home!
